divs: Sighting DetailsI went out on my balcony for a cigarette break, saw an object traveling from the west, headed in an eastern direction. There was no exhaust trail, no noise, seemed to be moving at a steady (fast speed), with no decline in altitude level. ***Here are the last 3 photos (Magnify the area in the center of the Red circular highlight to see the object).
